1
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:46,790
Commander.

2
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:49,130
The Emperor's orders cannot be disobeyed.

3
00:00:49,130 --> 00:00:50,800
It's an assassination mission.

4
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:51,700
Dead or alive.

5
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:59,560
Helan Ci.

6
00:01:01,060 --> 00:01:03,560
You transferred the troops from Anding Gate to stop me.

7
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,530
Do you know that

8
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,430
before Yu Henian died,

9
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:09,490
he gave the capital's defense map to the barbarians?

10
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:28,630
Fire the arrows!

11
00:01:28,630 --> 00:01:29,890
Fire the arrows for me!

12
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,530
He is just bluffing.

13
00:01:31,830 --> 00:01:33,400
Kill this traitor!

14
00:01:40,830 --> 00:01:41,800
Ying Wujiu.

15
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,200
You really didn't disappoint me.

16
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:46,600
Even my imperial guards couldn't stop you.

17
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,600
You brought your troops back.

18
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:52,060
Do you want to see me beg for mercy on my knees,

19
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:54,500
or do you want me to give you the dragon robe?

20
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:58,100
Your Majesty, the flank of Anding Gate is unguarded.

21
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:58,800
The scouts reported that

22
00:01:58,800 --> 00:01:59,800
the barbarians have breached the pass.

23
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:00,800
I brought the troops back

24
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:01,660
not for treason,

25
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:03,230
but to enter the city and fight the enemy.

26
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,200
Fight the enemy.

27
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,830
I will defend my own empire.

28
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:10,830
If you want to take Jingzhi away,

29
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:13,190
it will be over my dead body.

30
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:16,490
Otherwise, even if you flatten this Meridian Gate,

31
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:19,730
you can only take away my Imperial Noble Consort.

32
00:02:34,829 --> 00:02:35,660
Jingzhi.

33
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:38,760
I thought I could win against him once.

34
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:40,600
But I forgot that

35
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:44,430
the Emperor of Dazheng shouldn't gamble with Dazheng's gates.

36
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:52,060
Ying Wujiu, catch the sword and enter the city!

37
00:03:01,730 --> 00:03:02,960
Kill!

38
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:27,860
Jingzhi.

39
00:03:28,730 --> 00:03:29,860
This last time,

40
00:03:30,930 --> 00:03:33,060
I have chosen a way of survival for you.

41
00:03:57,230 --> 00:04:00,030
Kill!

42
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:04,030
Dazheng's empire

43
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:06,290
is not a place for you animals to run wild.

44
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:06,960
Ying Wujiu!

45
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:08,700
I have said it.

46
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:10,060
What is mine,

47
00:04:10,930 --> 00:04:12,460
I will personally protect.

48
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:19,000
Since Your Majesty wants to be crazy,

49
00:04:19,230 --> 00:04:20,130
I will accompany you.

50
00:04:20,130 --> 00:04:21,230
For this last time.

51
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:33,830
Your Majesty!

52
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:36,030
Ying Wujiu.

53
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:37,530
Don't mind me.

54
00:04:38,230 --> 00:04:39,530
Kill them all.

55
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:42,960
Jingzhi is watching from the city tower.

56
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,860
Don't embarrass me.

57
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:49,700
Hyah!

58
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,330
Kill!

59
00:04:58,130 --> 00:04:59,030
Helan Ci.

60
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:05,830
Jingzhi.

61
00:05:06,230 --> 00:05:07,060
Don't cry.

62
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:11,000
I have always forced you my whole life.

63
00:05:11,230 --> 00:05:12,360
For this last time...

64
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,460
For this last time,

65
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:16,800
I allow you to live the life you want.

66
00:05:17,730 --> 00:05:18,930
Ying Wujiu.

67
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:21,300
I have defended the empire,

68
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:22,920
and I have returned her

69
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,930
to you.

70
00:05:29,230 --> 00:05:30,230
Commander.

71
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:33,760
Now the royal bloodline is withering.

72
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,430
Only if you ascend the throne

73
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:38,000
can you stabilize the world

74
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:41,000
and suppress this mess.

75
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:44,500
This chair is stained with too many people's blood

76
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,400
and has trapped too many souls.

77
00:05:48,730 --> 00:05:49,230
I

78
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,360
do not care for it.

79
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:00,300
This empire

80
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:02,130
was defended by Helan Ci with his life.

81
00:06:02,130 --> 00:06:03,060
Protect it well.

82
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,700
If you ever become a tyrant,

83
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,230
even if I am no longer in the martial world,

84
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:09,560
the blades of this world

85
00:06:09,930 --> 00:06:11,260
will return at any time.

86
00:06:26,730 --> 00:06:27,500
Ying Wujiu,

87
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,930
do you regret it?

88
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:31,460
That is the supreme position of the world.

89
00:06:41,030 --> 00:06:41,760
Jingzhi.

90
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,260
Living this life again

91
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:46,800
was never about the world.

92
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:50,400
All my fighting and scheming

93
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,130
was just for this moment,

94
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:55,630
to watch this sunset with you.

95
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:57,159
Dedicated to all those who look up at the light from the abyss.
